    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This vehicle has plenty of character and is ready for someone with a vision to give it some TLC! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle with great potential at a very accessible price point.",
